    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-02-16</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-04-26T17:55:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Congress Must Co-Sign Act of 2007 - Directs the Secretary of Transportation to provide advance written notice to Congress before any Department of Transportation (DOT) funds may be used to make a loan in the amount of $1 billion or more. Prohibits DOT from making such loan until Congress has enacted a law specifically approving the loan.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
